BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:ZC4P-VwJeSZvvnJ4tGT5k
SUMMARY:THIS IS FOR YOU: An Improvised Theatre Poetry Experience
DTSTAMP:20260325T193738Z
DTSTART:20260405T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Step into a world where your memories spark the unexpected\\\, 
	your objects tell untold stories\\\, and your life becomes art in motion. 
	With a swirl of spontaneous theater\\\, hand-typed poetry\\\, and the soul
	ful sounds of live musicians\\\, each night unfolds like a dream—unrepeata
	ble\\\, electric\\\, and uniquely yours. One moment\\\, you’re laughing at
	 a scene born from a trinket in your pocket\; the next\\\, a poem crafted 
	just for you finds its way into your hands. This is poetry in motion. This
	 is music in the moment. This is theater made from the fabric of your life
	. Come laugh. Come cry. Come as you are. \\n✨ THIS IS FOR YOU! ✨ \\nDon’t 
	miss this once-in-a-lifetime fusion of words\\\, sound\\\, and improvisati
	on. April is the month of poetry—come celebrate the magic!\n\nhttps://www.
	unexpectedproductions.org/event/this-is-for-you-an-improvised-theatre-poet
	ry-experience-4-2-2/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/this-is-for-you-an-improvis
	ed-theatre-poetry-experience-4-2-2/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions Market Theater\\\, 1428 Post Alley\\\, Seat
	tle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
